Typo Enclosure on Steroide
==========================

Typo Enclosure on Steroide displays an article attachments at the end of the post, eventually using specific view according to file type.

Currently, supported type are :
* MP3, using Dew mp3 player


Example
=======

To include Typo Enclosure on Steroide into your Typo template, edit the view/_article.html.erb file, and add the following code at the place you want to display your attachments:

<%= display_resources(article) %> 


